<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />They crush your people, Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">they afflict the nation that belongs to you.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />They kill the widow and foreigner who lives in their country,</para>

<para style="q1">and they murder the fatherless.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />They say, "Yahweh will not see,</para>

<para style="q1">the God of Jacob does not take notice of it."</para>
